== Using CPAN modules without the pain

* Want to use a CPAN module which you don't have installed
+* Can't build the CPAN module cos you don't have the shared lib installed
+* Need root to instal modules and local::lib is not available
+* behind a firewall and can't get to the CPAN
+* Use RemoteLib!

